</style></meta></meta></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 40px;"><a href="http://bit.ly/ccxVyf">Downcast: Critically endangered bahaba caught and sold for $500,000</a>&nbsp;</p>  <p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 40px;"><a href="http://bit.ly/d4YXTz ">Green ideas: How to Recycle Your Old CDs and DVDs</a> </p>  <p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 40px;"><a href="http://bit.ly/cNLw9G">Clint Eastwood's Orangutan Sidekick Still a Hero </a></p>  <p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 40px;"><a href="http://bit.ly/bxeYM2">Keith Olbermann Helps Raise $250,000 for Storm-Ravaged Cheyenne River Reservation </a></p>  <p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 40px;"><a href="http://bit.ly/dBxuMY">Soldier explores PTSD by drawing graphic novel </a></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 40px;"><a href="http://bit.ly/9Q6TxH">Spend Green: Do Business with the World's Greenest Companies</a> </p><p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 40px;"><a href="http://bit.ly/c9zR1Y">Romanticism undone: Invasive species, global warming taking toll on plants at Thoreau's Walden Pond</a> <br />&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Oh, and here are two old reviews that I&nbsp;wrote for Joe Bob Briggs several years ago.&nbsp;He's revamping his site and they have popped back up.</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 40px;"><a href="http://tinyurl.com/y8872fx">Belly Button Comix </a></p>  <p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 40px;"><a href="http://is.gd/87w66">Mighty Skullboy Army </a></p>  <p style="margin-bottom: 0in; margin-left: 80px;">&nbsp;</p> <div style="margin-left: 40px;">&nbsp;</div>That's it for now. Back to the netbook!
